short_description:
Main target of this project - create opensource SDK to communicate with AR.Drone 2.0 (http://ardrone2.parrot.com/). Project are based on Qt/С++ library 4.x.x and so it crossplatform =)
Thus, subtargets of this project:
  - create opensource and crossplatform SDK;
  - create set of UI-classes to visualize drone's data and control it;
  - create test GUI-application.
